{"tid":452503,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[LIHKG]粵語配音討論(13)","createTime":"2017-10-30T09:40:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-06T11:06:10.000Z","uid":20914,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7d44d6820fb58c5623c96988b03666837fe1cf13","tid":452503,"uid":20914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T09:40:24.000Z","msg":"本區設於動漫台，以討論於香港免費電視台播放之粵語配音動畫(及其週邊、原作 etc)為主 <br />\n討論劇集／綜藝節目／吹水為副  <br />\n開post既temp:<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1wShw2MV5Fyje0Tp2Rsgkb5QUm5ZbA1uXOoqO3UAaQdo/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1wShw2MV5Fyje0Tp2Rsgkb5QUm5ZbA1uXOoqO3UAaQdo%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=jpN7jgqLyokpm27jydmuRTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=688cc2ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1wShw2MV5Fyje0Tp2Rsgkb5QUm5ZbA1uXOoqO3UAaQdo/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n------討論重點-----<br />\n曹啟謙好靚仔<br />\n伍博民好鬼萌<br />\n黃啟昌一字馬<br />\n梁偉德你好嘢<br />\n奇妙電視loop舊動畫 但係冇網上重溫 有鬼用<br />\n港台電視應該買多啲動畫<br />\n香港電視網絡快啲攞到牌啦<br />\nViuTV唔好半途而廢<br />\n希望J2唔使播賽馬 六合彩"},{"pid":"a8a4e1febee2b70e6b2634b76579e7da3615efb5","tid":452503,"uid":20914,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T09:41:26.000Z","msg":"------討論紀錄------<br />\n#1 12034<br />\n#2 70348<br />\n#3 102194<br />\n#4 131001<br />\n#5 155697<br />\n#6 182517<br />\n#7 207745<br />\n#8 224178<br />\n#9 240849<br />\n#10 285142<br />\n<br />\n#11 359860<br />\n#12 411691<br />\n#13 452503"},{"pid":"6fe956f127cce617a45a733ba87384b32e477933","tid":452503,"uid":20914,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T09:42:23.000Z","msg":"---香港免費電視頻道 粵語配音動畫及特攝節目時間表---<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1LS1RKx0RBfRgPz-noMZ9Iaal0fpJZlUZCL5VTuqgvr8/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1LS1RKx0RBfRgPz-noMZ9Iaal0fpJZlUZCL5VTuqgvr8%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dshar